data.description: Located at the base of Grand Mesa in a pleasant in-town neighborhood, this well built home WITH extra garage/shop, fenced backyard and mature landscaping is just waiting for you.  Efficient considerations with a newly installed 4kw solar system, metal roof, vinyl windows and sliding doors, plus attic fan and motorized awning for passive cooling.  Large living room with wood stove insert and open Dining/Kitchen areas.  Bedrooms located on raised half-level.  Spacious attached garage plus 1-car carport, and a 20' x 14' detached shop on a concrete slab.  Front and back lawns with sprinkler systems, plus roses, forsythia bushes and 2 dwarf apple trees.  Enjoy the spacious back yard and the 2 person hot tub.  This property maximizes it's space and offers plenty of garage storage for your toys!  Welcome home...
